Text: "5 may 2016 de wich main and mere 3 friend Kheer Ganga nu Jan lyi tyar hoye\
  \ Kheer Ganga ik himachal pardesh wich hai\nkheer ganga jithe shiv parvati ne bhagti\
  \ kiti\nis jgha te harr saal hajara yatri aonde hann\nRaste de wich sbh toh pehla\
  \ asin mandi wich ruke jithe Sikha de 10 ve Guru shiri guru gobind singh de palang\
  \ Ravav majood hi jo ke ik bht e paviter jgha hi is Mahan jgah de Darshan toh baad\
  \ asin Mani karan sahib wala Ruk kita Jithe sikha de pehle guru shiri guru Nanak\
  \ sahib ji ne adbut chamatkar kita ublde pani wich langar tyar kita\nMani karan\
  \ de darshan krn uprant asi 3 Din kheer ganga wal tayri khichi\neh jgha mani karan\
  \ sahb toh 12 kilomiter di doori te hai\nKhoobsurat pahriya nal giriya hoya 12 kilomiter\
  \ agge da rasta ho padal tur ke jana painda hi\nfir main and mere dosta ne safar\
  \ shuru kita\nrastede wich asin photos\nselfis\nlyia\nkhoob surat jharne mann moh\
  \ rahe san\nfr   thora safar karan toh baad asin cha pini chahi\njithe baith ke\
  \ asin cha \nand biskut kahe\ncha peen toh baad asin aage da safar shuru kita karib\
  \ 4 pm te asin apni manjil te ponch gye\nfir kuch time aram karan toh baa othe te\
  \ haseen mosam da mzha lea\nachanak us jgha te barish shuru ho gi\nhill area krke\
  \ mosam kde thk ho jnda kde khrab ho jnda\nfir asin othe tent buy kita raat rehan\
  \ lyi asin apne nal old monk di rum b le k gye c\nso raat time asin lovely lovely\
  \ peg lgaye and othe de raat time da satalite view dekh k bhat anad miliya\n2ji\
  \ saver asin 8 k wjhede karib othe waps aon lyi ture\napne friend's nal ehtho waps\
  \ aonde hoye hasde khedde aisn kheer ganga toh waps manikarn sahb a ke ruke\nfir\
  \ aram karn toh baad aisn apne ghr waps a gye\neh mera trip innha yaadgar reha ke\
  \ main is trip nu thode nal share krke bht khushi hoi"
